+// upstream-u2 (Phase 10): mutex-protect the lazy schema cache.  The
+// original DCL-without-lock pattern is unsafe when multiple threads or
+// reentrant calls hit get_schema() before populate completes.  A
+// function-local C++11 magic-static would be cleanest, but clear_schema()
